04:23:56.380 --> 04:24:05.380
[Guest]: but I think that's also the fun of this podcast that you allow people to ramble and then you find things to kind of from that,

04:24:05.380 --> 04:24:09.380
[Guest]: whatever from that long kind of ramble.

